WEBVTT

00:00.452 --> 00:04.248
_

00:04.288 --> 00:05.636
There was war.

00:05.734 --> 00:08.602
We knew that there had been
people killed up there.

00:11.378 --> 00:12.478
But there was something

00:12.513 --> 00:14.580
just completely wrong
about this place.

00:18.151 --> 00:20.620
I never, ever believed
in ghosts before.

00:26.093 --> 00:28.227
Did we unleash something?

00:32.165 --> 00:33.743
Someone is trying to kill us.

00:35.202 --> 00:36.602
It's gonna be them or me.

00:37.971 --> 00:39.739
And it's sure as hell
not gonna be me.

00:39.773 --> 00:41.107
Let's go.

00:41.141 --> 00:42.729
What do you do?

00:42.762 --> 00:44.443
I mean, you have this gun

00:44.478 --> 00:45.878
and all this gear.

00:47.614 --> 00:49.615
But that's not
gonna help you now.

00:50.481 --> 00:51.717
Go, go, go, go!

00:53.854 --> 00:55.273
We're all about to die
right now.

